00:13:45,748 --> 00:13:46,548
Go and make an interview.

288
00:13:46,748 --> 00:13:47,588
Find out what they have to say.

289
00:13:47,948 --> 00:13:48,188
Okay.

290
00:13:50,468 --> 00:13:51,308
Have you changed your fragrance?

291
00:13:52,708 --> 00:13:53,348
It smells good.

292
00:13:54,748 --> 00:13:55,668
It may be the sample

293
00:13:55,868 --> 00:13:57,148
given by my friend.

294
00:13:57,388 --> 00:13:58,468
I'll gift it to you
when it goes on sale.

295
00:13:58,708 --> 00:13:59,028
Sure.

296
00:14:13,708 --> 00:14:14,428
Xiaoran.

297
00:14:16,628 --> 00:14:17,548
You haven't come for a long while.

298
00:14:19,268 --> 00:14:20,668
Where's Qingshan's press conference?

299
00:14:21,428 --> 00:14:22,988
The ballroom is on the left
after exiting the door.

300
00:14:29,828 --> 00:14:30,268
Xiaoran.

301
00:14:36,668 --> 00:14:37,108
Xiaoran.

302
00:14:38,948 --> 00:14:39,308
Can you stay out

303
00:14:39,508 --> 00:14:40,308
of this matter?

304
00:14:44,348 --> 00:14:44,628
Why?

305
00:14:45,228 --> 00:14:45,948
Have I got in your way?

306
00:14:46,548 --> 00:14:47,668
I'm sorry.

307
00:14:47,948 --> 00:14:49,388
Not only do I have to look into this,

308
00:14:49,668 --> 00:14:50,788
I also want to do a series of reports

309
00:14:50,988 --> 00:14:51,868
and follow-ups.

310
00:14:58,548 --> 00:14:59,708
(Conference on transforming and upgrading)
Thanks again to journalists

311
00:14:59,708 --> 00:14:59,908
(Conference on transforming and upgrading)

312
00:14:59,908 --> 00:15:01,548
(Conference on transforming and upgrading)
who attend the press conference about

313
00:15:01,548 --> 00:15:01,708
(of Qingshan Nursing Home)

314
00:15:01,708 --> 00:15:03,468
(of Qingshan Nursing Home)
transforming Qingshan Nursing Home.

315
00:15:03,668 --> 00:15:04,948
Due to the short notice,

316
00:15:05,108 --> 00:15:05,988
we aren't in time

317
00:15:06,148 --> 00:15:07,468
to prepare tags for all of you.

318
00:15:07,628 --> 00:15:08,628
Please take your seats.

319
00:15:15,060 --> 00:15:17,340
(Conference on transforming and upgrading
of Qingshan Nursing Home)

320
00:15:21,748 --> 00:15:22,308
Hello, everyone.

321
00:15:22,828 --> 00:15:24,028
I'm Xiao Shangqi.

322
00:15:24,508 --> 00:15:25,868
I'm the new director

323
00:15:26,068 --> 00:15:26,788
of Qingshan Nursing Home.

324
00:15:28,988 --> 00:15:30,748
The agreement of transfer
has been signed.

325
00:15:31,188 --> 00:15:32,308
Relevant procedures

326
00:15:32,468 --> 00:15:33,588
are in orderly progress.

327
00:15:33,748 --> 00:15:35,268
I'll take charge

328
00:15:35,748 --> 00:15:36,708
of Qingshan's affairs.

329
00:15:37,508 --> 00:15:39,988
You should've read the news.

330
00:15:40,268 --> 00:15:41,628
After the transfer is complete,

331
00:15:41,988 --> 00:15:43,188
Qingshan Nursing Home

332
00:15:43,348 --> 00:15:45,108
will be transformed into Qingshan Hotel.

333
00:15:45,908 --> 00:15:46,308
Although

334
00:15:46,468 --> 00:15:47,428
we serve a different group of people,

335
00:15:48,028 --> 00:15:49,588
I still hope

336
00:15:49,788 --> 00:15:51,548
to continue the spirit of Qingshan.

337
00:15:51,748 --> 00:15:53,268
That's to stay away
from hustle and bustle,

338
00:15:53,428 --> 00:15:54,148
blend in the nature

339
00:15:54,508 --> 00:15:55,348
to heal the body and mind.

340
00:15:59,508 --> 00:16:00,028
May I know

341
00:16:00,588 --> 00:16:01,308
how you'll rehouse

342
00:16:01,508 --> 00:16:03,228
the 57 elderly people

343
00:16:03,388 --> 00:16:04,748
currently staying at
Qingshan Nursing Home

344
00:16:04,948 --> 00:16:05,868
and what's the duration?

345
00:16:06,068 --> 00:16:07,108
We're also concerned about

346
00:16:07,268 --> 00:16:08,668
a proper rehousing
of the elderly people.

347
00:16:09,148 --> 00:16:09,708
I'd

348
00:16:10,028 --> 00:16:11,148
further increase the compensation

349
00:16:11,348 --> 00:16:12,108
by 30%.

350
00:16:12,508 --> 00:16:13,948
For those with difficulty,

351
00:16:14,108 --> 00:16:15,268
I'd offer a temporary stay
in Jifeng Hotel

352
00:16:15,428 --> 00:16:16,348
for free

353
00:16:16,708 --> 00:16:17,348
until they find

354
00:16:17,548 --> 00:16:18,508
a suitable place.

355
00:16:18,748 --> 00:16:20,108
Has your latest proposal

356
00:16:20,348 --> 00:16:20,868
received

357
00:16:21,028 --> 00:16:22,188
their approval?

358
00:16:22,468 --> 00:16:23,428
Or

359
00:16:23,668 --> 00:16:25,108
is this merely your self-moving

360
00:16:25,388 --> 00:16:26,748
or self-persuasion?

361
00:16:27,188 --> 00:16:27,588
That's right.

362
00:16:27,828 --> 00:16:28,148
How will you

363
00:16:28,308 --> 00:16:29,108
rehouse the elderly people?

364
00:16:29,468 --> 00:16:30,188
Will there be other choices

365
00:16:30,268 --> 00:16:31,428
if they refuse to come to Jifeng?

366
00:16:35,828 --> 00:16:36,708
Time is limited for us.

367
00:16:36,948 --> 00:16:37,548
Shall we shorten

368
00:16:37,668 --> 00:16:38,788
the questioning session a bit?

369
00:16:42,188 --> 00:16:43,188
One will think from

370
00:16:43,348 --> 00:16:44,388
his or her own perspective.

371
00:16:45,388 --> 00:16:46,828
What the elderly people think

372
00:16:47,228 --> 00:16:48,468
is to live the most comfortable

373
00:16:48,628 --> 00:16:50,148
later life

374
00:16:50,308 --> 00:16:51,508
with the least money

375
00:16:51,588 --> 00:16:52,428
but in the steadiest way.

376
00:16:52,588 --> 00:16:53,308
But from a more macro

377
00:16:53,468 --> 00:16:54,348
perspective,

378
00:16:54,908 --> 00:16:57,228
Qingshan Nursing Home is a company.

379
00:16:57,428 --> 00:16:58,988
Profit is the essence of business.

380
00:16:59,188 --> 00:17:00,108
Qingshan has been in the red

381
00:17:00,308 --> 00:17:01,228
for seven quarters.

382
00:17:01,628 --> 00:17:03,068
If it goes on losing,

383
00:17:03,548 --> 00:17:04,708
that will be irresponsible
to the employees

384
00:17:04,908 --> 00:17:06,428
and the community.

385
00:17:06,748 --> 00:17:08,108
Closing down in a week

386
00:17:08,348 --> 00:17:09,908
may sound rather hasty,

387
00:17:10,148 --> 00:17:11,267
but this is the result of a combination

388
00:17:11,468 --> 00:17:12,668
of commercial considerations.

389
00:17:12,908 --> 00:17:13,588
I got it.

390
00:17:14,027 --> 00:17:15,108
The starting point

391
00:17:15,267 --> 00:17:16,787
of your solution is commercial interest.

392
00:17:16,908 --> 00:17:18,828
Everything has to give way
to money, right?

393
00:17:18,868 --> 00:17:20,908
One percent of the quarterly profit

394
00:17:21,068 --> 00:17:22,828
made by Qingshan Hotel in the future

395
00:17:23,188 --> 00:17:24,988
will be donated to
nursing homes in the city.

396
00:17:25,988 --> 00:17:27,787
We'll use our best way

397
00:17:27,868 --> 00:17:29,188
to fulfil social obligations

398
00:17:29,548 --> 00:17:30,628
and deliver

399
00:17:30,828 --> 00:17:32,788
greater social benefits to everyone.

400
00:17:34,148 --> 00:17:34,788
This measurement

401
00:17:34,988 --> 00:17:35,348
sounds good.

402
00:17:35,548 --> 00:17:36,188
It's certainly not bad.

403
00:17:36,348 --> 00:17:37,348
It's good to the society.

404
00:17:40,188 --> 00:17:41,428
I still have one last question.

405
00:17:42,108 --> 00:17:43,908
Yunlan is based in Hupu.

406
00:17:44,268 --> 00:17:44,668
Mr. Xiao,

407
00:17:45,228 --> 00:17:45,668
why do you want

408
00:17:45,868 --> 00:17:47,188
to leave the major battlefield alone

409
00:17:47,388 --> 00:17:49,748
and choose to expand
business opportunities in Wusu?

410
00:17:52,228 --> 00:17:54,788
Hupu is the red ocean
of business competition

411
00:17:55,348 --> 00:17:56,268
so I want to be

412
00:17:56,468 --> 00:17:58,308
a forerunner in the blue ocean of Wusu.

413
00:17:58,828 --> 00:18:00,388
I happen to get a chance

414
00:18:00,548 --> 00:18:01,708
to take over Qingshan.

415
00:18:01,948 --> 00:18:02,908
The wetland on Damang Mountain

416
00:18:03,108 --> 00:18:03,948
is exceptionally beautiful.

417
00:18:04,388 --> 00:18:05,988
I personally like this place
in particular.

418
00:18:06,428 --> 00:18:07,788
In my heart,

419
00:18:08,388 --> 00:18:08,748
this

420
00:18:09,588 --> 00:18:11,188
is a Xanadu.

421
00:18:20,748 --> 00:18:21,948
Do you still have other questions?

422
00:18:25,388 --> 00:18:26,508
We've prepared refreshment

423
00:18:26,708 --> 00:18:28,068
for the media people.

424
00:18:28,228 --> 00:18:28,868
If you need it,

425
00:18:29,028 --> 00:18:30,548
please proceed to enjoy it
in the lounge area.

426
00:18:30,788 --> 00:18:31,388
Thank you, everyone.

427
00:18:44,708 --> 00:18:45,548
Xiaoran,

428
00:18:45,948 --> 00:18:46,788
it's been a long while.

429
00:18:47,348 --> 00:18:48,708
Will you dine here tonight?

430
00:18:49,148 --> 00:18:49,628
I'll ask Meng to

431
00:18:49,748 --> 00:18:50,548
prepare sweet and sour ribs for you.

432
00:18:50,788 --> 00:18:51,628
Save the trouble.

433
00:18:53,788 --> 00:18:54,628
I know.

434
00:18:54,828 --> 00:18:55,508
You aren't on the same page

435
00:18:55,628 --> 00:18:57,068
as him over this matter,

436
00:18:57,508 --> 00:18:57,988
but...

437
00:18:58,228 --> 00:18:59,068
You're He Xiaoran, right?

438
00:18:59,508 --> 00:19:01,028
I'm Nuo, the hostess of City News.

439
00:19:01,188 --> 00:19:02,388
I finally meet you in person.

440
00:19:02,748 --> 00:19:03,868
I have listeners exposing

441
00:19:03,948 --> 00:19:05,468
some social issues to me lately.

442
00:19:05,668 --> 00:19:06,268
I'd like to get your advice

443
00:19:06,348 --> 00:19:07,308
on how to deal with it.

444
00:19:08,468 --> 00:19:09,308
Just teach me.

445
00:19:16,388 --> 00:19:17,228
I see.

446
00:19:17,308 --> 00:19:18,468
I should talk to you more.

447
00:19:18,828 --> 00:19:19,228
Xiaoran,

448
00:19:19,388 --> 00:19:20,308
let me make a cup of coffee for you.

449
00:19:20,948 --> 00:19:22,108
You don't need to.

450
00:19:23,908 --> 00:19:25,148
How do I use this?

451
00:19:29,548 --> 00:19:30,228
Thank you, Mr. Xiao.

452
00:19:43,068 --> 00:19:44,188
Be careful, it's hot.

453
00:19:48,908 --> 00:19:49,508
Thank you.

454
00:20:03,108 --> 00:20:04,068
It's nice.

455
00:20:04,508 --> 00:20:05,708
There're two of us.

456
00:20:05,908 --> 00:20:07,348
Aren't you going to make
another cup for Miss He?

457
00:20:08,468 --> 00:20:09,948
I suppose she can make one for herself.

458
00:20:10,268 --> 00:20:10,828
Yes.

459
00:20:11,988 --> 00:20:13,068
But I'm sick of drinking it.

460
00:20:14,908 --> 00:20:15,548
Miss He,

461
00:20:16,268 --> 00:20:17,708
are you satisfied with our solution?

462
00:20:18,748 --> 00:20:19,348
Mr. Xiao,

463
00:20:19,948 --> 00:20:20,828
is your solution

464
00:20:21,068 --> 00:20:22,068
meant to brush us away

465
00:20:22,188 --> 00:20:23,628
or to solve the problem?

466
00:20:24,348 --> 00:20:24,868
You shouldn't ask

467
00:20:24,988 --> 00:20:25,508
if I'm satisfied or not.

468
00:20:25,988 --> 00:20:26,868
You should ask the elderly people

469
00:20:26,988 --> 00:20:27,788
in Qingshan.

470
00:20:41,570 --> 00:20:42,500
(Yunlan Jifeng Hotel)

471
00:20:51,188 --> 00:20:51,908
Why are you here?

472
00:20:52,948 --> 00:20:54,068
Hui proposes to dine together.

473
00:20:54,268 --> 00:20:54,908
I came to pick you up.

474
00:20:55,348 --> 00:20:56,428
I met Lili just now.

475
00:20:56,508 --> 00:20:57,668
She said you've come to Jifeng.

476
00:20:58,508 --> 00:20:59,508
Qingshan's press conference.

477
00:21:00,668 --> 00:21:01,748
Has the thick-skinned Xiao Shangqi

478
00:21:01,908 --> 00:21:02,588
come back to find you?

479
00:21:04,508 --> 00:21:05,988
Elderly people of the nursing home

480
00:21:06,068 --> 00:21:07,668
sought help from me.

481
00:21:07,948 --> 00:21:08,988
I came to do a follow-up.

482
00:21:09,348 --> 00:21:10,628
You exposed him with a news report.

483
00:21:10,708 --> 00:21:12,228
He struck back with a press conference.

484
00:21:12,468 --> 00:21:13,228
When will you stop

485
00:21:13,428 --> 00:21:14,428
fighting each other?

486
00:21:16,708 --> 00:21:17,268
We're not fighting.

487
00:21:20,228 --> 00:21:20,788
Xiaoran,

488
00:21:22,228 --> 00:21:22,948
you have someone to pick you up.

489
00:21:24,628 --> 00:21:24,948
Mo.

490
00:21:25,588 --> 00:21:26,428
Where's Mr. Xiao?

491
00:21:27,508 --> 00:21:28,308
He's busy.

492
00:21:29,188 --> 00:21:29,428
All right.

493
00:21:29,628 --> 00:21:30,588
Pass him the message for me.

494
00:21:31,268 --> 00:21:31,948
Since he's back,

495
00:21:32,148 --> 00:21:33,348
he should focus on his career

496
00:21:33,628 --> 00:21:34,348
and stay away from us.

497
00:21:35,508 --> 00:21:35,948
Enough.

498
00:21:36,788 --> 00:21:38,428
Xiaoran, I'm going back to work.

499
00:21:42,428 --> 00:21:42,788
It's just

500
00:21:42,948 --> 00:21:44,308
a work crossover.

501
00:21:44,508 --> 00:21:45,148
You sounded like

502
00:21:45,148 --> 00:21:46,188
I care about it so much.

503
00:21:47,028 --> 00:21:48,548
It's best if you don't care.

504
00:21:49,148 --> 00:21:50,308
He gave you up.

505
00:21:50,508 --> 00:21:52,028
Since he's made a choice,

506
00:21:52,508 --> 00:21:53,388
it means many things

507
00:21:53,588 --> 00:21:54,468
have changed.

508
00:21:56,628 --> 00:21:57,908
Isn't it just about rehousing
the elderly people?

509
00:21:57,948 --> 00:21:58,788
Tell me how many of them.

510
00:21:58,908 --> 00:21:59,548
I'll figure it out for you.

511
00:22:00,068 --> 00:22:01,108
Stay away from him.

512
00:22:03,628 --> 00:22:04,268
You're right.

513
00:22:05,228 --> 00:22:05,868
Instead of fighting a war of words,

514
00:22:06,068 --> 00:22:06,988
I should do something practical.

515
00:22:07,788 --> 00:22:08,508
I should look for

516
00:22:08,668 --> 00:22:10,348
an institution that
meets the conditions.

517
00:22:12,148 --> 00:22:12,588
Let's go.

518
00:22:13,628 --> 00:22:14,508
Let's go for dinner.

519
00:22:15,660 --> 00:22:27,000
(Yunlan Jifeng Hotel)

520
00:22:37,068 --> 00:22:37,628
You've finally come.

521
00:22:38,388 --> 00:22:40,028
Everyone's glass is empty.

522
00:22:40,428 --> 00:22:41,068
We're waiting for you.

523
00:22:41,588 --> 00:22:42,348
Okay, let me.

524
00:22:44,028 --> 00:22:44,708
Hello.

525
00:22:44,948 --> 00:22:45,308
Let me.

526
00:22:45,508 --> 00:22:46,308
No worries. I'm on it.

527
00:22:47,348 --> 00:22:47,948
Did I call for you?

528
00:22:50,588 --> 00:22:51,588
I love to drink

529
00:22:51,908 --> 00:22:53,148
wine served by Xiao Xian.

530
00:22:55,788 --> 00:22:56,908
Mr. Zhao, while you're abroad

531
00:22:57,108 --> 00:22:58,188
for two weeks,

532
00:22:58,748 --> 00:22:59,748
were you unable

533
00:22:59,948 --> 00:23:00,708
to cope without

534
00:23:00,908 --> 00:23:01,988
having Xian to serve a drink?

535
00:23:02,508 --> 00:23:03,748
I don't like what you're saying.

536
00:23:04,268 --> 00:23:05,548
Xiao Xian knows how to do

537
00:23:05,748 --> 00:23:06,108
a lot of things.

538
00:23:09,908 --> 00:23:10,308
By the way,

539
00:23:10,988 --> 00:23:12,788
how's Qi lately?

540
00:23:15,068 --> 00:23:16,868
He couldn't close any deal.

541
00:23:17,348 --> 00:23:18,508
As promised,

542
00:23:18,748 --> 00:23:21,028
he's left Yunlan.

543
00:23:22,628 --> 00:23:24,068
What a waste of effort.

544
00:23:24,268 --> 00:23:25,668
At least Xian is sensible.

545
00:23:26,188 --> 00:23:26,828
Otherwise,

546
00:23:27,108 --> 00:23:27,708
Yunlan

547
00:23:27,908 --> 00:23:29,468
might probably be brought down with him.

548
00:23:29,708 --> 00:23:30,268
Don't you agree?

549
00:23:33,148 --> 00:23:33,828
He should've

550
00:23:34,028 --> 00:23:35,148
returned to Wusu,

551
00:23:35,348 --> 00:23:36,588
hiding in his girlfriend's arms.

552
00:23:36,828 --> 00:23:38,148
I reckon he's crying.

553
00:23:42,068 --> 00:23:43,468
I heard this from someone.

554
00:23:44,708 --> 00:23:45,468
He mortgaged Jifeng

555
00:23:45,668 --> 00:23:47,028
after returning to Wusu.

556
00:23:47,308 --> 00:23:49,188
He's acquired a nursing home

557
00:23:49,388 --> 00:23:50,708
on Damang Mountain.

558
00:23:51,988 --> 00:23:53,668
Nursing home on Damang Mountain?

559
00:23:53,988 --> 00:23:55,188
Was it the hotel sold by Deju

560
00:23:55,348 --> 00:23:56,508
several years ago?

561
00:23:59,548 --> 00:24:00,468
I'm surprised

562
00:24:01,228 --> 00:24:01,748
that he loves to pick up

563
00:24:01,748 --> 00:24:02,788
things unwanted by me.

564
00:24:03,268 --> 00:24:03,708
Right.

565
00:24:04,588 --> 00:24:05,348
Go to the golf club on my behalf

566
00:24:05,508 --> 00:24:06,548
tomorrow.

567
00:24:06,708 --> 00:24:07,988
Deliver an agreement to Mr. Gao.

568
00:24:08,188 --> 00:24:09,508
If he wants to play,

569
00:24:09,748 --> 00:24:11,388
you may be his company.

570
00:24:11,628 --> 00:24:13,708
But I don't know about golf

571
00:24:13,908 --> 00:24:15,188
and it's not convenient for me.

572
00:24:15,588 --> 00:24:16,068
Why not...

