861
00:37:15,988 --> 00:37:17,108
to settle you down.

862
00:37:17,308 --> 00:37:17,748
Settle down?

863
00:37:18,028 --> 00:37:18,988
Don't get it wrong.

864
00:37:19,268 --> 00:37:20,148
I don't want here

865
00:37:20,188 --> 00:37:21,308
to be transformed.

866
00:37:21,468 --> 00:37:22,348
Yes.

867
00:37:22,428 --> 00:37:23,468
We won't go anywhere.

868
00:37:23,548 --> 00:37:24,468
I don't want to move.

869
00:37:24,628 --> 00:37:25,508
If I move,

870
00:37:25,908 --> 00:37:26,868
my son can't find me

871
00:37:27,068 --> 00:37:28,468
when he comes back.
I don't want to move.

872
00:37:28,508 --> 00:37:29,428
- I don't want to move.
- Madam.

873
00:37:29,988 --> 00:37:30,548
I don't want to move.

874
00:37:30,548 --> 00:37:31,268
Take it easy.

875
00:37:31,268 --> 00:37:31,908
We're figuring out a way.

876
00:37:31,908 --> 00:37:32,508
Not moving is never

877
00:37:32,508 --> 00:37:33,188
an option.

878
00:37:34,468 --> 00:37:35,428
The renovation will start

879
00:37:35,788 --> 00:37:37,028
on the day of closing it down.

880
00:37:37,308 --> 00:37:39,028
I advise all of you to be wiser.

881
00:37:39,468 --> 00:37:40,788
Take the compensation the soonest.

882
00:37:41,188 --> 00:37:42,508
Go and find a suitable nursing home.

883
00:37:42,988 --> 00:37:44,068
Rascal,

884
00:37:44,348 --> 00:37:46,508
you're young but wicked.

885
00:37:46,508 --> 00:37:47,948
You're terrible.

886
00:37:49,948 --> 00:37:50,308
Mr. Sun.

887
00:37:51,148 --> 00:37:51,708
Be careful.

888
00:37:52,668 --> 00:37:53,228
What's going on?

889
00:37:55,028 --> 00:37:56,268
Make a call.

890
00:37:56,548 --> 00:37:57,068
He's fainted.

891
00:37:57,348 --> 00:37:57,828
Make the call now.

892
00:37:57,868 --> 00:37:58,348
Do it.

893
00:37:59,148 --> 00:38:00,948
I'm going to make a call.

894
00:38:01,708 --> 00:38:02,788
Hello, is this 120?

895
00:38:02,788 --> 00:38:03,628
Hurry up! Phone!

896
00:38:03,668 --> 00:38:04,400
Hurry up!

897
00:38:04,400 --> 00:38:04,588
(Emergency)
Hurry up!

898
00:38:04,588 --> 00:38:07,000
(Emergency)

899
00:38:11,588 --> 00:38:12,508
You're quite steady.

900
00:38:13,268 --> 00:38:14,228
You'll be held accountable

901
00:38:14,508 --> 00:38:15,308
if anything happens to Mr. Sun.

902
00:38:17,748 --> 00:38:18,308
Mr. Sun.

903
00:38:18,308 --> 00:38:18,868
How are you?

904
00:38:19,828 --> 00:38:20,388
Hurry up!

905
00:38:21,588 --> 00:38:21,948
Mr. Sun.

906
00:38:22,348 --> 00:38:22,828
I feel bad.

907
00:38:23,348 --> 00:38:23,828
Mr. Sun.

908
00:38:25,588 --> 00:38:26,988
You said you've explored
some nursing homes.

909
00:38:27,508 --> 00:38:28,508
Are you helping me to rehouse them?

910
00:38:28,708 --> 00:38:30,228
Don't flatter yourself.

911
00:38:30,628 --> 00:38:31,748
I just want to make good use
of the time

912
00:38:31,908 --> 00:38:32,668
by doing something practical.

913
00:38:38,108 --> 00:38:38,828
Can you postpone

914
00:38:39,108 --> 00:38:40,148
the day of closing down by a month?

915
00:38:41,228 --> 00:38:42,188
It takes a day

916
00:38:42,348 --> 00:38:43,188
for two young people

917
00:38:43,188 --> 00:38:44,068
to visit five nursing homes.

918
00:38:44,348 --> 00:38:45,548
They all are aged.

919
00:38:45,828 --> 00:38:47,108
How will they possibly settle down

920
00:38:47,188 --> 00:38:48,308
in three days?

921
00:38:48,708 --> 00:38:49,348
Two of you?

922
00:38:50,948 --> 00:38:51,908
You and Sui Mingwei?

923
00:38:52,428 --> 00:38:53,388
Is there a problem?

924
00:38:56,228 --> 00:38:56,628
Thank you

925
00:38:56,788 --> 00:38:57,708
for working so hard to help me,

926
00:38:58,388 --> 00:38:58,868
but can you

927
00:38:59,028 --> 00:39:00,148
stay out of this?

928
00:39:00,428 --> 00:39:01,268
I have my own arrangement.

929
00:39:01,548 --> 00:39:02,468
Don't flatter yourself.

930
00:39:02,868 --> 00:39:03,868
It's not you whom I care.

931
00:39:07,828 --> 00:39:08,348
Doctor.

932
00:39:08,548 --> 00:39:09,268
What's his condition?

933
00:39:09,668 --> 00:39:10,588
He has some chronic diseases,

934
00:39:10,828 --> 00:39:12,548
but they aren't the causes
of this fainting.

935
00:39:12,908 --> 00:39:14,148
His ECG is quite normal.

936
00:39:14,308 --> 00:39:15,148
Do you want to

937
00:39:15,348 --> 00:39:16,308
put him under observation

938
00:39:16,588 --> 00:39:17,708
or take him home to rest?

939
00:39:18,388 --> 00:39:19,348
Rascal,

940
00:39:19,628 --> 00:39:20,748
I want some fruits!

941
00:39:21,628 --> 00:39:22,788
He has good spirit and appetite.

942
00:39:23,068 --> 00:39:23,908
Advise him

943
00:39:24,108 --> 00:39:24,908
to go home early and rest.

944
00:39:24,948 --> 00:39:25,428
Thank you, doctor.

945
00:39:25,468 --> 00:39:25,988
You're welcome.

946
00:39:26,068 --> 00:39:26,748
Thank you.

947
00:39:29,548 --> 00:39:30,108
Mr. Xiao.

948
00:39:30,428 --> 00:39:31,268
We're lucky this time.

949
00:39:31,428 --> 00:39:32,068
It's a close call.

950
00:39:32,628 --> 00:39:33,308
You should know

951
00:39:33,468 --> 00:39:34,148
you're facing a group of

952
00:39:34,268 --> 00:39:35,908
elderly people in their 70s or 80s.

953
00:39:36,708 --> 00:39:37,748
I understand that
you want to do business

954
00:39:37,948 --> 00:39:38,708
and make money,

955
00:39:39,308 --> 00:39:40,428
but the elderly people

956
00:39:40,628 --> 00:39:41,308
have limited physical

957
00:39:41,308 --> 00:39:42,228
and mental capacity.

958
00:39:42,508 --> 00:39:43,068
Some of them may really collapse

959
00:39:43,188 --> 00:39:44,308
one day.

960
00:39:47,508 --> 00:39:48,548
What attitude is that?

961
00:39:48,828 --> 00:39:49,748
Behave yourself.

962
00:39:58,770 --> 00:40:04,340
(Wusu Shenghe Hospital)

963
00:40:06,748 --> 00:40:07,308
Mr. Xiao.

964
00:40:07,908 --> 00:40:08,668
Mr. Xiao.

965
00:40:09,228 --> 00:40:10,108
I'm going to deliver

966
00:40:10,308 --> 00:40:11,148
fruits to Mr. Sun.

967
00:40:11,468 --> 00:40:11,988
Go ahead.

968
00:40:12,268 --> 00:40:12,948
Okay.

969
00:40:15,068 --> 00:40:16,108
Mr. Sun turns out

970
00:40:16,268 --> 00:40:16,988
to feign an illness.

971
00:40:17,268 --> 00:40:18,268
He's hospitalised for a day.

972
00:40:18,508 --> 00:40:19,828
What a trick.

973
00:40:20,708 --> 00:40:21,508
He wants to draw attention.

974
00:40:22,068 --> 00:40:22,828
Let him be.

975
00:40:23,188 --> 00:40:23,908
If you asked me,

976
00:40:24,148 --> 00:40:25,108
he's the opinion leader

977
00:40:25,268 --> 00:40:26,028
in the group.

978
00:40:26,228 --> 00:40:26,868
He's the hardest to deal with.

979
00:40:27,988 --> 00:40:29,428
If we can make him move out,

980
00:40:29,548 --> 00:40:30,468
the rest will move out

981
00:40:30,628 --> 00:40:31,148
very quickly.

982
00:40:31,468 --> 00:40:34,708
Shall we approach his family
to figure out a way?

983
00:40:36,308 --> 00:40:37,308
He has no children, right?

984
00:40:37,748 --> 00:40:38,748
He has no children,

985
00:40:39,108 --> 00:40:40,188
but he has a nephew.

986
00:40:40,388 --> 00:40:41,828
He'd come to visit him on holidays.

987
00:40:42,068 --> 00:40:42,828
Mr. Sun

988
00:40:42,868 --> 00:40:43,708
seems indifferent,

989
00:40:43,908 --> 00:40:44,908
but he's nice to his nephew.

990
00:40:45,108 --> 00:40:46,028
He treats his nephew like his own son.

991
00:40:46,508 --> 00:40:47,108
It's fine.

992
00:40:48,308 --> 00:40:50,228
We should still begin with compensation.

993
00:40:51,028 --> 00:40:51,628
Take him

994
00:40:51,828 --> 00:40:53,028
to visit a few more nursing homes

995
00:40:53,588 --> 00:40:54,540
until he likes one of them.

996
00:40:56,708 --> 00:40:57,868
We should hit where it hurts.

997
00:40:58,028 --> 00:40:59,228
Don't do anything useless.

998
00:40:59,388 --> 00:41:00,668
Give his nephew some benefits.

999
00:41:00,828 --> 00:41:01,948
It can be settled at once.

1000
00:41:02,828 --> 00:41:03,428
It's not honourable

1001
00:41:03,588 --> 00:41:04,628
to use money already.

1002
00:41:05,268 --> 00:41:06,668
There's no need to
make use of gratitude.

1003
00:41:07,788 --> 00:41:08,468
Mr. Xiao.

1004
00:41:09,748 --> 00:41:10,508
I can't figure you out

1005
00:41:10,668 --> 00:41:11,508
sometimes.

1006
00:41:11,828 --> 00:41:13,348
A while ago, you seemed
to be a businessman

1007
00:41:13,548 --> 00:41:14,628
who only recognises money and agreement.

1008
00:41:14,828 --> 00:41:16,188
After that, you show a bit of humanity.

1009
00:41:17,548 --> 00:41:18,308
I'm going up

1010
00:41:18,468 --> 00:41:19,268
to persuade Mr. Sun.

1011
00:41:19,508 --> 00:41:20,468
Sure.

1012
00:41:20,468 --> 00:41:24,440
(Wusu Shenghe Hospital)

1013
00:41:43,610 --> 00:41:46,540
(Nomination of the Newsmaker
of the Year, He Xiaoran)

1014
00:41:57,948 --> 00:41:58,988
In just a few months,

1015
00:41:59,188 --> 00:42:00,388
you got ten breaking news.

1016
00:42:00,388 --> 00:42:01,588
The average rating is above seven.

1017
00:42:01,788 --> 00:42:03,268
You live up to

1018
00:42:03,308 --> 00:42:04,628
the Newsmaker of the Year.

1019
00:42:05,308 --> 00:42:06,108
Lili.

1020
00:42:06,228 --> 00:42:07,468
Of course, it's just nomination for now.

1021
00:42:07,468 --> 00:42:08,348
It's yet to be announced,

1022
00:42:08,748 --> 00:42:09,628
but I've seen

1023
00:42:09,628 --> 00:42:10,668
the voting results.

1024
00:42:11,028 --> 00:42:12,468
Just wait to receive

1025
00:42:12,668 --> 00:42:14,108
the award at the annual
recognition night of journalists

1026
00:42:14,188 --> 00:42:15,028
two days later.

1027
00:42:15,748 --> 00:42:16,668
Thank you, Lili.

1028
00:42:16,788 --> 00:42:17,908
Why do you thank me?

1029
00:42:18,108 --> 00:42:19,188
You should thank yourself.

1030
00:42:19,388 --> 00:42:20,548
You definitely can become

1031
00:42:20,548 --> 00:42:21,908
an exceptional journalist.

1032
00:42:22,228 --> 00:42:22,788
Sure.

1033
00:42:25,468 --> 00:42:26,428
RMB 3,500 in total for this month.

1034
00:42:26,588 --> 00:42:27,108
I've transferred it.

1035
00:42:27,308 --> 00:42:28,068
Thank you, Hao.

1036
00:42:29,428 --> 00:42:30,468
Hui,

1037
00:42:30,828 --> 00:42:31,868
do you really want

1038
00:42:32,028 --> 00:42:32,748
to sing here

1039
00:42:32,828 --> 00:42:33,708
forever?

1040
00:42:33,948 --> 00:42:34,708
Is it meaningful to make petty money

1041
00:42:34,908 --> 00:42:36,028
as a part-timer?

1042
00:42:36,868 --> 00:42:37,548
Are you sick of my singing,

1043
00:42:37,668 --> 00:42:38,268
so you want to replace me?

1044
00:42:38,348 --> 00:42:39,388
No, don't overthink it.

1045
00:42:39,388 --> 00:42:40,188
It's surely not.

1046
00:42:40,308 --> 00:42:41,188
I think

1047
00:42:42,188 --> 00:42:43,748
you're quite talented.

1048
00:42:44,028 --> 00:42:45,668
It's a waste of talent
singing at my place.

1049
00:42:46,108 --> 00:42:47,148
Is it a waste of talent

1050
00:42:47,268 --> 00:42:48,348
singing at your place?

1051
00:42:48,588 --> 00:42:49,148
What a joke.

1052
00:42:49,268 --> 00:42:49,868
No.

1053
00:42:49,948 --> 00:42:50,668
Give it a good thought.

1054
00:42:50,748 --> 00:42:51,588
I mean it.

1055
00:42:52,748 --> 00:42:53,508
See you, Hao.

1056
00:42:57,028 --> 00:42:57,588
Well,

1057
00:42:58,148 --> 00:42:59,668
Hao is right.

1058
00:43:00,868 --> 00:43:01,628
How long do you want

1059
00:43:01,788 --> 00:43:03,108
to work as a part-timer here?

