♪The lonely man has been waiting♪

1064
00:43:36,922 --> 00:43:42,562
♪Afraid of hearing
that we're just friends♪

1065
00:43:42,562 --> 00:43:47,762
♪Many excuses after turning around♪

1066
00:43:47,762 --> 00:43:55,842
♪Turning around in the time♪

1067
00:43:56,922 --> 00:43:59,602
♪Running towards the road of memory♪

1068
00:43:59,602 --> 00:44:02,202
♪I've been searching for so long♪

1069
00:44:02,202 --> 00:44:06,962
♪Found the wait that I owed you♪

1070
00:44:06,962 --> 00:44:09,882
♪Wanting to be with you♪

1071
00:44:09,882 --> 00:44:12,842
♪No more alone and wandering♪

1072
00:44:12,842 --> 00:44:18,602
♪I'd like to hold your hands
